#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L03_RintroRcases
msgid "# Pattern-Matching Introduction: rintro and rcases\n"
"\n"
"In Level 2, the proof of the image property took four steps:\n"
"В§0, В§1, В§2, then work.\n"
"\n"
"Lean offers a power tool that collapses this: **В§3**. It combines\n"
"В§4 with deep pattern matching in a single step. The key feature\n"
"is the **В§5 pattern**: when you write В§6 inside the pattern,\n"
"it automatically substitutes the equation instead of naming it.\n"
"\n"
"В§7\n"
"\n"
"For image membership В§8 (which is В§9),\n"
"this gives you:\n"
"- В§10 -- the witness\n"
"- В§11 -- the membership proof\n"
"- The equation В§12 is consumed by В§13, which replaces В§14\n"
"  with В§15 everywhere\n"
"\n"
"Compare the two approaches:\n"
"\n"
"| Steps | Old way | With rintro |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| 1 | В§16 | В§17 |\n"
"| 2 | В§18 | (done!) |\n"
"| 3 | В§19 | |\n"
"\n"
"The **В§20** tactic does the same pattern matching on an existing\n"
"hypothesis: В§21.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that if В§22 is in the image of the \"triple\"\n"
"function on numbers less than 4, then В§23. Use В§24 for\n"
"a two-step proof."
msgstr ""

