#: Game.Levels.PreimageWorld
msgid "# Preimage World\n"
"\n"
"Given a function В§0 and a set В§1 (a set of outputs),\n"
"the **preimage** of В§2 under В§3 is the set of all inputs whose output\n"
"lands in В§4:\n"
"\n"
"В§5\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this is written В§6 (type В§7).\n"
