"| Level 3 | This level |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| Predicate: В§1 (arithmetic) | Predicate: В§2 (existential) |\n"
"| В§3 unfolds to arithmetic | В§4 gets the existential |\n"
"| В§5 on the arithmetic | В§6 extracts witness, THEN В§7 |\n"
"\n"
"Notice the recurring pattern across Levels 2, 3, and this level: **unfold\n"
"the set notation, assume or provide, then close with arithmetic**. This is\n"
"the *membership reduction* pattern вҖ” every set membership question reduces\n"
"to a question about the underlying predicate, and the proof works directly\n"
"with that predicate. This pattern transfers to every set concept in this\n"
"course.\n"
"\n"
"The В§8 tactic is your tool for destructuring existentials. Whenever\n"
"you have В§9, use В§10 to get the witness\n"
"В§11 and the proof В§12. You will use this pattern throughout the\n"
"course вҖ” it appears whenever set membership involves existential\n"
"conditions."
msgstr ""

