#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld
msgid "# Image World\n"
"\n"
"You have mastered preimages -- pulling sets back through functions. Now you\n"
"will study the dual operation: **images** -- pushing sets forward.\n"
"\n"
"Given a function В§0 and a set В§1 (a set of inputs),\n"
"the **image** of В§2 under В§3 is the set of all outputs that come from\n"
"inputs in В§4:\n"
"\n"
"В§5\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this is written В§6 (type В§7).\n"
"\n"
"**The critical difference from preimage**: Image membership involves an\n"
"**existential**. To prove В§8, you must **exhibit a witness** --\n"
"an input В§9 such that В§10. Preimage membership was just\n"
"function application (В§11 -- no witness needed).\n"
"Image membership requires a construction.\n"
"\n"
"This existential has far-reaching consequences:\n"
"- Image preserves union: **yes** (equality)\n"
"- Image preserves intersection: **no** (only вҠҶ, not =)\n"
"- Image preserves complement: **no**\n"
"\n"
"Compare with preimage, which preserves ALL set operations. The\n"
"difference comes down to logic: preimage uses В§12, В§13, В§14 which\n"
"commute with function application. Image uses В§15, which does NOT\n"
"commute with В§16 or В§17.\n"
"\n"
"By the end of this world, you will:\n"
"- Prove image membership by exhibiting witnesses\n"
"- Learn В§18 and В§19 -- power tools for pattern matching\n"
"- Prove В§20 -- the vacuous extremal case\n"
"- Prove В§21 -- the simplest image\n"
"- Prove image preserves union but NOT intersection\n"
"- See a concrete counterexample for intersection equality\n"
"- Prove image distributes over function composition\n"
"- Learn В§22 -- the image of everything\n"
"- Prove that В§23\n"
"- Prove the Galois connection: В§24\n"
"- Explore the image-preimage gaps and when they close\n"
"- Re-derive monotonicity AND the image-preimage gap from the Galois connection\n"
"- Prove image preserves nonemptiness (both directions)\n"
"\n"
"The boss asks you to prove that В§25 when every element\n"
"of В§26 is in the range of В§27 -- the image-preimage gap closes with a\n"
"surjectivity condition.\n"
"\n"
"**New notation**: В§28 (typed В§29) -- the image of В§30 under В§31.\n"
"\n"
"**New tactics**: В§32 and В§33 -- pattern-matching introduction\n"
"and case analysis. You will also use В§34 (from Set World) extensively\n"
"with a new pattern: В§35.\n"
"\n"
"**Prerequisites**: Set World, Subset World, Set Operations World,\n"
"Preimage World."
msgstr ""

