#: Game.Levels.PreimageWorld.L08_PreimageIntersection
msgid "# Conjunction Passes Through\n"
"\n"
"Here is the first major structural result: preimage distributes over\n"
"intersection.\n"
"\n"
"В§0\n"
"\n"
"Why? An element В§1 is in the left side when В§2, which\n"
"means В§3. The right side says В§4 and\n"
"В§5, which means В§6 and В§7. These are the\n"
"same condition!\n"
"\n"
"The conjunction В§8 passes through function application unchanged.\n"
"This is the reason preimage \"preserves\" intersection.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. В§9 вҖ” reduce to membership\n"
"2. В§10 вҖ” split the В§11\n"
"3. **Forward**: В§12, destructure with В§13, reassemble\n"
"4. **Backward**: same in reverse"
msgstr ""

