#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L06_EmptySet
msgid "# The Empty Set\n"
"\n"
"The **empty set** В§0 is the set with no elements.\n"
"Its predicate is В§1 вҖ” it returns В§2 for every input.\n"
"\n"
"So В§3 reduces to В§4. Since В§5 has no proof,\n"
"nothing can ever be a member of В§6.\n"
"\n"
"Your task is to prove that NO natural number belongs to В§7. The\n"
"statement is В§8.\n"
"\n"
"The proof has two layers:\n"
"1. В§9 вҖ” introduce the universally quantified В§10\n"
"2. В§11 вҖ” since В§12 is В§13 which is В§14,\n"
"   introduce the hypothesis В§15\n"
"3. Now В§16 has type В§17 (since В§18 reduces to В§19),\n"
"   and the goal is В§20, so В§21 finishes.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove the statement step by step."
msgstr ""

