"\n"
"Both directions are trivially true because membership in В§1 is\n"
"always В§2. There are no witnesses in the empty set, so the\n"
"existential in image membership is vacuously false.\n"
"\n"
"**The vacuous existential**: В§3 is always false\n"
"regardless of В§4, because there is no В§5 in В§6. This is the\n"
"foundational reason why В§7.\n"
"\n"
"**Extremal cases**: Image sends the two extreme sets to:\n"
"- В§8 (this level)\n"
"- В§9 (Level 12)\n"
"\n"
"Compare with preimage: В§10 and В§11.\n"
"Image of everything depends on the function (its range), while\n"
"preimage of everything is always everything. Another manifestation\n"
"of the image-preimage asymmetry.\n"
"\n"
"The library name is В§12."
