msgid "# Dual De Morgan: (s вҲ© t)б¶ң = sб¶ң вҲӘ tб¶ң\n"
"\n"
"In Level 12, you proved В§0. Now prove the\n"
"**dual**: the complement of an intersection is the union of the\n"
"complements:\n"
"\n"
"В§1\n"
"\n"
