"- В§3 witnesses В§4\n"
"\n"
"But В§5 because ANY single witness would need to be\n"
"in BOTH В§6 and В§7 -- and В§8 is empty.\n"
"\n"
"**The root cause**: The constant function collapses В§9 and В§10 to\n"
"the same output. The intersection of images uses different witnesses\n"
"for the same output, while the image of intersection demands a single\n"
"witness that works for both sets.\n"
"\n"
"**The injectivity connection**: If В§11 were injective, the two\n"
"witnesses would have to be equal (since В§12 would\n"
"imply В§13). So injectivity prevents this kind of phantom\n"
"intersection. You will prove В§14 for\n"
"injective В§15 in a later world.\n"
"\n"
"**Complement fails too**: The same existential-vs-universal issue\n"
"means image does not preserve complement either: В§16 and\n"
"В§17 have no inclusion in either direction in general. Preimage\n"
"preserves complement exactly (В§18) because\n"
"negation commutes with function application, but image's existential\n"
"does not commute with negation."
msgstr ""

