#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L18_Boss
msgid "# Boss: Chaining Subsets to Prove Equality\n"
"\n"
"You have two sets В§0 and В§1 of natural numbers, with three\n"
"hypotheses:\n"
"- В§2 вҖ” В§3 is contained in В§4\n"
"- В§5 вҖ” В§6 is contained in the numbers at most 4\n"
"- В§7 вҖ” every number less than 5 is in В§8\n"
