"Think about what this means. The hypothesis В§10 tells you that\n"
"В§11. And from В§12 and В§13, you can chain:\n"
"В§14. Since В§15 is the same as В§16 for\n"
"natural numbers, this gives В§17. Together with\n"
"В§18, you get equality by antisymmetry.\n"
"\n"
"This problem integrates the core skills of this world:\n"
"- **В§19 or В§20** to prove equality\n"
"- **В§21** to prove subsets\n"
"- **В§22/В§23** to unwrap set membership\n"
"- **Chaining subset hypotheses** (transitivity from Level 8)\n"
"- **В§24** to bridge arithmetic facts\n"
"\n"
"There are multiple valid strategies. Choose your own path!"
