#: Game.Levels.PreimageWorld.L16_Boss
msgid "Congratulations вҖ” you completed **Preimage World** by composing\n"
"your library of results!\n"
"\n"
"The proof was just four rewrites:\n"
"1. В§0 вҖ” difference is intersection with complement\n"
"2. В§1 вҖ” preimage distributes over В§2\n"
"3. В§3 вҖ” preimage distributes over В§4\n"
"4. В§5 вҖ” repackage as difference\n"
"\n"
"No В§6, no В§7, no case analysis. You used previously\n"
"proved theorems as building blocks. This is the payoff of having\n"
"a library: each new result becomes easier because you can stand on\n"
"your earlier work.\n"
"\n"
"## The Complete Preimage Library\n"
"\n"
"You have built a complete theory. Here is everything you proved,\n"
"in one place:\n"
"\n"
"| Level | Identity | Logic | Library name |\n"
"|---|---|---|---|\n"
"| L05 | В§8 | monotonicity | В§9 |\n"
"| L06 | В§10 | В§11 | В§12 |\n"
"| L07 | В§13 | В§14 | В§15 |\n"
"| L08 | В§16 | В§17 | В§18 |\n"
"| L09 | В§19 | В§20 | В§21 |\n"
"| L10 | В§22 | В§23 | В§24 |\n"
"| L11 | В§25 | В§26 | В§27 |\n"
"| L12 | В§28 | В§29 | В§30 |\n"
"| L13 | В§31 | identity | В§32 |\n"
"| L14 | В§33 | composition | В§34 |\n"
"| L16 | В§35 | В§36 + В§37 | В§38 |\n"
"\n"
"Every row says the same thing: **preimage is a Boolean algebra\n"
"homomorphism**. It maps the Boolean algebra of subsets of В§39\n"
"(with В§40, В§41, В§42, В§43, В§44) into the Boolean algebra\n"
"of subsets of В§45, preserving all operations. It is also\n"
"**contravariant** вҖ” it reverses the direction of function\n"
"composition (L14).\n"
"\n"
"The single structural reason: preimage is just composition on the\n"
"predicate level. В§46 is В§47. Composing with\n"
"В§48 does not change the logical connectives inside В§49.\n"
"\n"
"**The topology connection**: In topology, a function В§50 is defined\n"
"to be **continuous** if and only if the preimage of every open set\n"
"is open. The preservation results you proved here are exactly why\n"
"this definition works вҖ” continuous functions automatically preserve\n"
"all the set-theoretic structure that topology needs.\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: In Image World, you will study В§51 вҖ”\n"
"the image of a set under a function. Image involves an existential\n"
"(В§52), and existentials do NOT\n"
"commute with conjunction or negation. Image only preserves union,\n"
"not intersection or complement. The contrast between the\n"
"well-behaved preimage and the less-well-behaved image is one of\n"
"the central themes of this course."
msgstr ""

