"reverse В§22 is **false** вҖ” the number 4 is in\n"
"the right set but not the left. You will prove this formally in\n"
"Level 7. So В§23 has a *direction*: unlike equality, В§24 does\n"
"not imply В§25. This makes В§26 a one-way relationship, which\n"
"we will explore further in this world."
