msgid "# Powerset Is Monotone\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you proved a concrete powerset membership. Now\n"
"prove that the powerset operation is **monotone**: if В§0, then\n"
"В§1.\n"
"\n"
"In words: every subset of В§2 is also a subset of В§3, because\n"
"being a subset of a smaller set is a stronger condition.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof strategy**: To show В§4, take an element В§5,\n"
"convert to В§6 using В§7, then use the hypothesis\n"
"В§8 to conclude В§9, and convert back.\n"
