"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. В§15 вҖ” split В§16 into В§17 and В§18\n"
"2. **First goal** (В§19): prove the subset as in Level 1\n"
"3. **Second goal** (В§20): disprove the reverse as in Level 7"
