#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L05_NonMembershipExistential
msgid "# Non-Membership with Existential Predicates\n"
"\n"
"In Level 3, you proved В§0 вҖ” the predicate was a simple\n"
"arithmetic comparison, and В§1 dispatched it directly after В§2.\n"
"\n"
"But what happens when the predicate involves an **existential**?\n"
"\n"
"The set В§3 has predicate В§4, which means\n"
"В§5. To prove В§6, you must show that\n"
"NO witness В§7 can satisfy В§8.\n"
"\n"
"The proof pattern:\n"
"1. В§9 вҖ” assume В§10, giving В§11\n"
"   (i.e., В§12)\n"
"2. В§13 вҖ” destructure the existential: extract the\n"
"   witness В§14 and the equation В§15\n"
"3. В§16 вҖ” the equation В§17 has no natural number solution\n"
"   (3 is odd), so В§18 derives В§19\n"
"\n"
"The new tactic here is В§20. It takes an existential hypothesis\n"
"and breaks it apart into its components. The syntax uses angle brackets:\n"
"В§21 (type вҹЁ as В§22 and вҹ© as В§23).\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that 3 is not even."
