#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L09_Boss
msgid "Congratulations вҖ” you have completed **SetWorld**!\n"
"\n"
"Here is what you now know:\n"
"\n"
"| Concept | Lean definition | Proof move |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Set | В§0 | вҖ” |\n"
"| Membership В§1 | В§2 (predicate evaluation) | unfolds automatically |\n"
"| Set builder В§3 | В§4 | unfolds to В§5 |\n"
"| В§6 | В§7 | В§8 |\n"
"| В§9 | В§10 | impossible (В§11) |\n"
"| В§12 | В§13 | В§14 with witness |\n"
"| Non-membership В§15 | В§16 | В§17 then contradiction |\n"
"| Compound predicate | В§18 | В§19 then prove each part |\n"
"\n"
"The central insight: **sets in Lean are predicates, and set operations\n"
"reduce to logical operations.** This principle extends throughout the\n"
"course: union will correspond to В§20, intersection to В§21, complement\n"
"to В§22, subset to В§23.\n"
"\n"
"In the next world, you will learn about **subsets** and **set equality**.\n"
"The key idea will be *extensionality*: two sets are equal when they have\n"
"the same elements, which means proving В§24. The\n"
"membership skills you just mastered are exactly what those proofs require."
msgstr ""

