#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L18_NonemptinessTransfer
msgid "# Nonemptiness Transfers Through Images\n"
"\n"
"If a set В§0 is nonempty, then its image В§1 is also nonempty.\n"
"This is intuitively obvious: if there is an element in В§2, applying\n"
"В§3 to it produces an element in В§4.\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, В§5 means В§6 -- there exists at\n"
"least one element. The proof pattern is different from the subset\n"
"and equality proofs you have been doing: instead of В§7/В§8,\n"
"you destructure the nonemptiness hypothesis to get a witness, then\n"
"build image membership from that witness.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. В§9 -- extract the witness from В§10\n"
"2. Construct В§11 using В§12 as the witness"
msgstr ""

