#: Game.Levels.IndexedOpsWorld.L17_IUnionEqualsUniv
msgid "# Indexed Union Covers Everything\n"
"\n"
"When a family of sets partitions the natural numbers, their indexed\n"
"union should be the entire universe. This level combines two tools\n"
"you have practiced separately:\n"
"\n"
"- В§0 to reduce a set equality to membership (from Subset World)\n"
"- В§1 to handle the indexed union (from this world)\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: The sets В§2 for В§3 partition\n"
"the natural numbers by remainder mod 3. Prove that their union is\n"
"В§4 вҖ” every natural number has *some* remainder mod 3.\n"
"\n"
"**About В§5 construction**: The index type here is В§6. To create\n"
"a В§7 value from a natural number В§8 known to satisfy В§9,\n"
"write В§10. For example, В§11 creates a valid\n"
"В§12 value because В§13 always holds. This angle-bracket\n"
"constructor packages a value with its proof of validity.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. В§14 вҖ” reduce to membership biconditional\n"
"2. В§15 вҖ” split the В§16\n"
"3. **Forward** (В§17): anything in a union is in В§18 (trivially)\n"
"4. **Backward** (В§19): given В§20, find its remainder class"
msgstr ""

