#: Game.Levels.IndexedOpsWorld.L01_IndexedUnion
msgid "# Indexed Unions\n"
"\n"
"In Set Operations World, you learned that В§0 corresponds to В§1:\n"
"an element is in the union if it is in В§2 **or** in В§3. But what if\n"
"you have not just two sets, but a whole **family** of sets вҖ” one for\n"
"each value of some index?\n"
"\n"
"If В§4 is a family of sets indexed by В§5, the\n"
"**indexed union** В§6 collects every element that belongs to\n"
"at least one set in the family:\n"
"\n"
"В§7\n"
"\n"
"The binary union В§8 is the special case with a two-element index\n"
"(В§9). The indexed version generalizes В§10 to В§11:\n"
"\n"
"| Operation | Notation | Logical meaning |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Binary union | В§12 | В§13 |\n"
"| Indexed union | В§14 | В§15 |\n"
"\n"
"**New tool**: В§16 converts В§17 into\n"
"В§18. After that, you provide the witness index with В§19.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: The family В§20 for В§21\n"
"gives one set for each possible remainder mod 3 (and more).\n"
"Prove that В§22 belongs to this indexed union by finding the right\n"
"remainder class."
msgstr ""

