"\n"
"In the previous level, you proved that indexed union is monotone:\n"
"if each В§0, then В§1. Now prove the\n"
"**dual** for indexed intersection:\n"
"\n"
"В§2\n"
"\n"
"The proof is simpler than the union case because there is no В§3\n"
