#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L04_EmptySubset
msgid "# Vacuous Truth: вҲ… вҠҶ s\n"
"\n"
"A fundamental fact in mathematics: the empty set is a subset of every set.\n"
"\n"
"В§0\n"
"\n"
"Why? Because В§1 means В§2. This is\n"
"**vacuously true**: the premise В§3 is always false (recall from\n"
"Set World that В§4 has predicate В§5), so the implication\n"
"holds no matter what В§6 is.\n"
"\n"
"After В§7, you will have В§8. Since В§9 is\n"
"definitionally В§10, the В§11 tactic can detect this\n"
"and close the goal immediately вҖ” regardless of what the goal is.\n"
"\n"
