#: Game.Levels.PsetImgPreimg.L07_InjectiveInterImage
msgid "You proved that injectivity closes the intersection gap!\n"
"\n"
"The proof had four key steps:\n"
"1. В§0 вҖ” destructure both\n"
"   image memberships\n"
"2. В§1 вҖ” apply injectivity to get В§2\n"
"3. В§3 вҖ” rewrite to get В§4\n"
"4. В§5 вҖ” build the image of the intersection\n"
"\n"
"**The witness collapse pattern**: Steps 2 and 3 are the defining proof\n"
"move for injectivity in image/preimage proofs. You have two witnesses\n"
"(В§6 and В§7) that map to the same output. Injectivity collapses them\n"
"into one (В§8), letting you combine their set memberships. Watch\n"
"for this pattern вҖ” you will use it in every remaining level.\n"
"\n"
"**Why does injectivity help?** If В§9, there\n"
"exist В§10 and В§11 with В§12. Without\n"
"injectivity, В§13 and В§14 might differ, so neither is in В§15.\n"
"With injectivity, В§16 forces В§17, so the single element\n"
"belongs to both В§18 and В§19.\n"
"\n"
"**Combined with В§20 from Image World**, you now have:\n"
"\n"
"В§21\n"
"\n"
"The \\\\subseteq direction (Image World L08) was unconditional; the\n"
"\\\\supseteq direction (this level) required injectivity.\n"
"\n"
"**The full biconditional**: This result is not just a sufficient\n"
"condition вҖ” injectivity is NECESSARY. If В§22\n"
"for ALL В§23, then В§24 must be injective. To see why: suppose\n"
"В§25. Take В§26 and В§27. Then\n"
"В§28 is nonempty, so by the equality\n"
"hypothesis В§29 is nonempty, which forces\n"
"В§30 to be nonempty, so В§31. In other words,\n"
"\"image preserves all binary intersections\" is a *characterization*\n"
"of injectivity, not just a consequence.\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: You will study В§32 extensively\n"
"in Injective World, where you will prove injectivity for specific\n"
"functions, compose injections, and extract injectivity from\n"
