#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L07_NonSubset
msgid "# When вҠҶ Fails: Proving В¬(s вҠҶ t)\n"
"\n"
"All the subset proofs so far have been **positive**: you showed that\n"
"one set is contained in another. But what if the containment is\n"
"**false**? How do you prove В§0?\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, В§1 is defined as В§2. So to prove В§3,\n"
"you use В§4 to **assume** the subset holds, getting\n"
"В§5, and then derive a contradiction (В§6).\n"
"\n"
"To derive the contradiction, exhibit a **counterexample**: find an\n"
"element that is in В§7 but not in В§8. If the subset held, this\n"
"element would have to be in both вҖ” but it is not, so we get В§9.\n"
"\n"
"In Level 1, we noted that В§10 is false\n"
"because 4 is in the first set but not the second. Now you will prove\n"
"this formally.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. В§11 вҖ” assume the subset holds (goal becomes В§12)\n"
"2. Prove В§13 вҖ” show the witness is in the domain\n"
"3. Apply В§14 to get В§15 вҖ” use the assumed subset\n"
"4. Unwrap and derive contradiction вҖ” В§16 is false"
msgstr ""

