#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L15_PreimageImageGap
msgid "The proof was just В§0 then В§1.\n"
"Constructing image membership with the same element you started with.\n"
"\n"
"**Why equality fails**: The reverse В§2 would\n"
"require: if В§3, then В§4. But В§5 only\n"
"means there exists SOME В§6 with В§7. If В§8 is not\n"
"injective, В§9 might differ from В§10, and В§11 might not be in В§12.\n"
"\n"
"**When does equality hold?** If В§13 is INJECTIVE: В§14\n"
"implies В§15, so В§16 gives В§17. You will prove this\n"
"in the problem set.\n"
"\n"
"**Summary of the two gaps**:\n"
"\n"
"| Statement | Holds? | Equality requires |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| В§18 | Always | Surjectivity onto В§19 |\n"
"| В§20 | Always | Injectivity of В§21 |\n"
"\n"
"The image-preimage gap and the preimage-image gap are controlled by\n"
"different properties of В§22. This asymmetry is one of the central\n"
"insights of this course.\n"
"\n"
"The library name is В§23."
msgstr ""

